  n      Get started n     RRC Cores RRC currently has    cores that specialize in various research techniques and areas  Furthermore  these cores maintain a diverse inventory of fully calibrated instruments available for users  Each core offers training on the use of instruments and core staff are equipped with skills and knowledge to troubleshoot equipment usage problems  RRC Cores are divided into three divisions  Bioanalytics  Biophysics   Cytomics Division nGenome Research Division nScientific Imaging   Nanotechnology Division Bioanalytics  Biophysics   Cytomics Division Genome Research Division Scientific Imaging   Nanotechnology Division  n      Learn more about our cores n     RRC Research Support Division In addition to the cores  RRC has a suite of Research Support Units  nScientific Computing Core nScientific Instrument Shop nScientific Storeroom nUI Health Biorepository Research Support Units Scientific Computing Core Scientific Instrument Shop Scientific Storeroom UI Health Biorepository  n      Learn more about our support units n     Google Maps image n     Research Resources Center Administrative Office rrcadmin uic edu http   www rrc uic edu  QUICK DIRECTORY  Bioanalytics    Cytomics Division  CfSB          S  Ashland Ave MSB E        South Wolcott Ave MBRB           S  Ashland Ave MSB E        South Wolcott Ave CfSB          S  Ashland Ave CMWT A         South Wolcott Ave MBRB           South Ashland Avenue CMWT A         South Wolcott Ave CMW           West Polk Street CMWT A         South Wolcott Ave COMRB           S  Wolcott Ave  Nanotechnology Division   MSB E C      S Wolcott Ave SES Suite          West Taylor St MSB Suite E        South Wolcott Ave      S Wolcott Ave ERF           W  Taylor St NMRL B        South Wood Street COMRB           S Wolcott Ave CMW           West Polk Street CSN W        S Wood St CMWT A         South Wolcott Ave MSB E         South Wolcott Ave  n      To find detailed directory  please click here n      n nUIC Log